### HOD API

@host = http://localhost:8080
@api = /api/hod

### --- PROFESSOR MANAGEMENT ---

### Create Professor
POST {{host}}{{api}}/professors
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "prof.smith@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "role": "PROFESSOR",
  "departmentId": 1
}

### Get All Professors
GET {{host}}{{api}}/professors?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Professor by ID
GET {{host}}{{api}}/professors/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Update Professor
PUT {{host}}{{api}}/professors/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice Updated",
  "lastName": "Smith Updated",
  "role": "PROFESSOR",
  "departmentId": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete Professor
DELETE {{host}}{{api}}/professors/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}


### --- DASHBOARD & REPORTS ---

### Get Dashboard Overview
GET {{host}}{{api}}/dashboard-overview?semesterId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get Submission Status Report
GET {{host}}{{api}}/submission-status?semesterId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}


### --- FILE EXPLORER ---

### Get File Explorer Root
GET {{host}}{{api}}/file-explorer/root?academicYearId=1&semesterId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get File Explorer Node
GET {{host}}{{api}}/file-explorer/node?path=some/path/to/folder
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}


### --- NOTIFICATIONS ---

### Get Notifications
GET {{host}}{{api}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Mark Notification as Read
POST {{host}}{{api}}/notifications/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
